comments: Lopez (MIL) slightly extends his arms outward as he establishes himself in a screening position in Adebayo's (MIA) path and marginal contact occurs as the pick is set.

Love (MIA) does not establish a legal guarding position and is still moving to his left into Antetokounmpo's (MIL) path when he initiates illegal body contact during Antetokounmpo's driving shot attempt.
Middleton (MIL) engages with Vincent (MIA) off-ball and marginal contact occurs as he releases away to retrieve the pass.
Vincent (MIA) extends his hand forward and makes clean contact with the ball to dislodge it away from Middleton (MIL) in the post.

Lopez's (MIL) arm comes backward, causing marginal upper-body contact to occur with Strus (MIA) as both players are moving toward the loose ball. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Adebayo (MIA) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Adebayo (MIA) and Lopez (MIL) briefly get tangled and marginal contact occurs as the two come together in the lane.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes a wide screening position when lower-body contact occurs with Holiday (MIL), which dislodges him during the pick.
Love (MIA) moves laterally into Middleton's (MIL) path and delivers body contact that affects his SQBR during the drive.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself and firms up over his left foot in Holiday's (MIL) path and marginal upper body contact occurs as the pick is set.
Lowry (MIA) reaches in and incidental hand-on-ball contact occurs with Middleton (MIL) as he dislodges the ball.
MIL asks for and is awarded the timeout before any potential contact from Adebayo (MIA) and Lowry (MIA).
Strus (MIA) commits a take foul on Holiday (MIL) in the backcourt.

Replay review of the foul called on Lowry (MIA) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Lowry (MIA) reaches in and cleanly deflects the ball away from Middleton (MIL). At the time of the whistle there was no possession, therefore the game will correctly resume with a jump ball.
Strus (MIA) extends his arms and marginal two hand contact occurs with Antetokounmpo (MIL) after he makes the intended pass.
Butler (MIA) commits a take foul on Holiday (MIL).
Connaughton (MIL) makes contact with Strus' (MIA) side during the inbound without affecting his SQBR.
Connaughton (MIL) holds Butler's (MIA) arm before Butler pushes off to receive the pass.
Middleton (MIL) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Vincent (MIA) and Middleton (MIL) both engage and separate in the lane.
Vincent (MIA) reaches in and makes contact with Middleton's (MIL) wrist during his upward shooting motion.
Matthews (MIL) swipes down and makes incidental hand-on-ball contact to dislodge it away from Butler (MIA) at the end of the drive.
Vincent (MIA) leans forward, creating marginal contact as Antetokounmpo (MIL) spins off it and continues toward the basket.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) steps forward into Strus' (MIA) space as he contests the shot and initiates lower-body contact as Strus is landing.
Middleton (MIL) brings his forearm to Vincent's (MIA) chest and marginal contact occurs as he releases away to retrieve the pass.
Vincent (MIA) avoids making contact to Middleton (MIL) as he legally contests the jump shot attempt.
Butler (MIA) beats Antetokounmpo (MIL) to the spot and marginal body contact occurs as the two come together during the drive.
